                                </h1>
                                <div class="arrow-link"
                                    onclick="window.open('/post/<%= pageData[pageData.length-2].slug %>', '_self')">
                                    <p style="color: #ffc300; font-size: 20px;">Read More</p>
                                    <img src="images/arrow.svg" alt="" class="arrow">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="blog-post" data-background-image="<%= pageData[pageData.length-3].data[5].data %>"
                            style="background-position: center; overflow-y: hidden; background-size: cover;">
                            <div
                                style="height: 398px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-end;  padding: 0px 40px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.403) 100%);">

